### 请求 /system/oauth2/authorize 接口 => 成功
GET {{baseUrl}}/system/oauth2/authorize?clientId=default
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
tenant-id: {{adminTenantId}}

### 请求 /system/oauth2/authorize + token 接口 => 成功
POST {{baseUrl}}/system/oauth2/authorize
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
tenant-id: {{adminTenantId}}

response_type=token&client_id=default&scope={"user.read": true}&redirect_uri=https://www.example.com&auto_approve=true

### 请求 /system/oauth2/authorize + code 接口 => 成功
POST {{baseUrl}}/system/oauth2/authorize
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
tenant-id: {{adminTenantId}}

response_type=code&client_id=default&scope={"user.read": true}&redirect_uri=https://www.example.com&auto_approve=false

### 请求 /system/oauth2/token + code 接口 => 成功
POST {{baseUrl}}/system/oauth2/token
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded
Authorization: Basic {{basicAuth}}
tenant-id: {{adminTenantId}}

grant_type=authorization_code&redirect_uri=https://www.example.com&code=189956c07a174588a97157eabef2f93a

### 请求 /system/oauth2/token + password 接口 => 成功
POST {{baseUrl}}/system/oauth2/token
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded
Authorization: Basic {{basicAuth}}
tenant-id: {{adminTenantId}}

grant_type=password&username={{username}}&password={{password}}&scope=user.read

### 请求 /system/oauth2/token + refresh_token 接口 => 成功
POST {{baseUrl}}/system/oauth2/token
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded
Authorization: Basic {{basicAuth}}
tenant-id: {{adminTenantId}}

grant_type=refresh_token&refresh_token={{refreshToken}}

### 请求 /system/oauth2/token + DELETE 接口 => 成功
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/system/oauth2/token?token={{token}}
Authorization: Basic {{basicAuth}}
tenant-id: {{adminTenantId}}

### 请求 /system/oauth2/check-token 接口 => 成功
POST {{baseUrl}}/system/oauth2/check-token?token={{token}}
Authorization: Basic {{basicAuth}}
tenant-id: {{adminTenantId}}
